### Description
Error "Object is possibly 'null'"
when ng serve and using getComputedStyle in code.


## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction
ng new project --strict

replace AppComponent to below 

```
export class AppComponent implements OnInit {
  title = 'test';

  ngOnInit() {
    const el = document.getElementById('test');
    if (el !== null) {
      // const paddingTop1 = window.getComputedStyle(el).paddingTop!; // this can work
      const paddingTop1 = window.getComputedStyle(el).paddingTop; // this can't work
      const paddingTopNumber1 = +paddingTop1; // TS2531: Object is possibly 'null'
      console.log(paddingTopNumber1);
    }
  }
}
```

ng serve --open

error will show

